<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Arbitrement" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Arbitrement,</orth> 1) decision: <cit><quote>incensed against you even to a mortal a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.286" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 286</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>if it come to the a. of swords,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.168" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 1, 168</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.89" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 89</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 7, 95</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.4.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 4, 52</bibl>.<lb />2) judicial inquiry: <cit><quote>we of the offering side must keep aloof from strict a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 1, 70</bibl></cit>.
